context: On <a0_0><b3_0>April 25, 2007<b3_0/><a0_0/>, <a1_0>Internet Archive<a1_0/> and <a2_0><b5_0>Suzanne Shell<b5_0/><a2_0/> jointly announced the settlement of their lawsuit. The <b4_0><b6_0><b7_0>Internet Archive<b7_0/><b6_0/><b4_0/> said it "...has no interest in including materials in the Wayback Machine of persons who do not wish to have their Web content archived.
